reviewText: Was the talk of the party.
This was purchased as a fun 50th  birthday gift!  Although I have not seen the DVD I will try to see it soon.  The gift went over well!

A great fun gift.  Perfect when you're not sure what to give someone.  It's interesting to see what was going on that year.  In the case of 1967, you'll see that what was going on then, is very like what's going on now.
